How to start the application
============================
1. Start com.github.networking.Server
2. com.sap.github.networking.Main is used to simulate three clients which connect to the server on port 4444

Protocol used for communication:
Client sends two separate messages to the server of the form:
1. "<client " + name + "> Hello Server"
Server responds with:
1. "<server> Hello Client\n"
2. "EOF"

When "<server> EOF" closes the client connection to the server 

How to build with maven 3
=========================
1. cd to Networking dir
2. mvn clean install
